ProtoTheorem:
. "Let $n_1, \ldots, n_k$ be positive integers. Then \[ 
   \prod_{i=1}^k {\mathbb Z}_{n_i} \cong {\mathbb Z}_{n_1 
   \cdots n_k} \] if and only if $\gcd( n_i, n_j) =1$ for $i 
   \neq j$."
